Class Match

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class Match
extends Region
implements java.lang.Comparable
    holds the result of a findX operation, is itself the region on the screen, where the image was found and hence inherits all methods from Region
    attributes:
    the match score (0 ... 1.0)
    the click target (e.g. from Pattern)
    the filename of the used image
    or the text used for findX text
